@startuml event-driven-signal-flow-lobby
!theme plain
!include ../shared/theme.puml
!include ../shared/sequence-theme.puml

title Event-Driven Signal Flow: Lobby and Connection Signals

participant "ConnectionManager\n(signal hub)" as Conn
participant "GDSync" as Sync

Conn -> Sync : subscribe to connected/lobby events\n(GDSync.connected, client_joined, etc.)
Sync -> Conn : emit connected/lobby updates
Conn -> Conn : re-emit via inner Signals class\n(player_joined_lobby, player_list_updated, ...)

note right of Conn
In-process event layer decouples
UI scenes from transport details.
Inner Signals class provides
namespaced signal re-emission.
end note

@enduml
